<!-- section:claude_summary -->
Home Assistant configuration for a two-person household (Cam and Enhy), running on HA OS. The system manages ~{{ '{:,}'.format(runtime) }} runtime entities across 14 domain packages, {{ custom_cc }} custom integrations, a token-driven UI design system, and Python automations. AI-assisted development uses cross-device session persistence (PC via Claude Desktop, tablet/phone via HA addon).
<!-- /section:claude_summary -->
<!-- section:claude_ha_version -->
- **HA version:** {{ core_ver }} on HA OS {{ os_ver }}
<!-- /section:claude_ha_version -->
<!-- section:claude_domain_table -->
| Domain | Files | Purpose | Key Entry Points |
|--------|-------|---------|-----------------|
| **ai** | {{ state_attr(pdb, 'ai_files') | int(0) }} | AI text/image generation, prompts, Claude bridge + Code Dispatch, Alexa TTS | `ai_main.yaml`, `claude_bridge.yaml`, `prompt_manager.yaml` |
| **communication** | {{ state_attr(pdb, 'communication_files') | int(0) }} | WhatsApp messaging, notifications, transcript pipeline | `whatsapp_config.yaml`, `alerts.yaml`, `transcript_pipeline.yaml` |
| **dashboard** | {{ state_attr(pdb, 'dashboard_files') | int(0) }} | Report viewer backend sensors | `report_viewer.yaml` |
| **device** | {{ state_attr(pdb, 'device_files') | int(0) }} | Cameras, covers/blinds, PC state, pet devices, Govee, Sonos | `cameras.yaml`, `curtains.yaml`, `pc.yaml` |
| **health** | {{ state_attr(pdb, 'health_files') | int(0) }} | Withings body composition metrics (C and E) | `health.yaml`, `weight.yaml` |
| **lights** | {{ state_attr(pdb, 'lights_files') | int(0) }} | Per-floor lighting automation with manual override | `lights.yaml`, `lights_office.yaml`, `auto_lights.yaml` |
| **network** | {{ state_attr(pdb, 'network_files') | int(0) }} | Device scanning, 63 MAC-to-device mappings | `ip_and_mac_address_mapping.yaml` |
| **occupancy** | {{ state_attr(pdb, 'occupancy_files') | int(0) }} | Presence detection (YAML anchors), doors, bed state, travel tracking | `presence_detection.yaml`, `doors.yaml`, `bed_state.yaml` |
| **server** | {{ state_attr(pdb, 'server_files') | int(0) }} | Git sync, frontend helpers, server stats, theme management | `github_sync.yaml`, `frontend/frontend_server_stats.yaml` |
| **shopping** | {{ state_attr(pdb, 'shopping_files') | int(0) }} | Shopping lists (Tesco/Amazon), supermarket busyness | `shopping_list.yaml`, `tesco_sensors.yaml` |
| **time** | {{ state_attr(pdb, 'time_files') | int(0) }} | Alarm tracking, hourly triggers, calendar event creation | `alarm_time.yaml`, `hourly_triggers.yaml` |
| **travel** | {{ state_attr(pdb, 'travel_files') | int(0) }} | Two-person location tracking, ETA, railway info | `map.yaml`, `railway.yaml` |
| **weather** | {{ state_attr(pdb, 'weather_files') | int(0) }} | Pirate Weather forecasts, AI clothing suggestions | `frontend_weather.yaml` |
| **work** | {{ state_attr(pdb, 'work_files') | int(0) }} | Meeting action extraction pipeline, AI classification | `work.yaml`, `work_actions_card.yaml` |
<!-- /section:claude_domain_table -->
